The quality of the images of this camera is really poor. There's quite a bit of movement which indicates that there were more hummingbirds, but all you can really see are blurs. Even in the better pictures it's difficult to identify the birds. Whether the problem is the age of the camera or light conditions or something else remains to be seen in the future.
